Auto-Submitted: auto-generated

***** Nagios/$VERSION$ *****

Host: $HOSTALIAS$
Address: $HOSTADDRESS$

$NOTIFICATIONTYPE$ :: $HOSTNAME$/$SERVICEDESC$ is $SERVICESTATE$
